text: Mitsuki Hashiguchi (born 14 February 1994) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2014 Asian Games and 2015 World Aquatic Championships. == References == == Other websites == * mitsuki-hashiguchi-of- japan-shoot * fina 1908 Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
